    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Transducers whose operation is based on magnetostriction, the change of length of a ferromagnetic substance when it is magnetized. They are used for the reception and transmission of high-frequency sound.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
